reviewText: Not as interesting as the more recent College Hill shows...
Thanks the video was in New condition. Received it in a timely manner. Very satisfied.

It was good to see College Hill do something different.  I did like the fact that the college kids were not able to just be on TV.  They actually have to work and show how serious they are about making it in the real world.  For me, the show seemed shorter than I remember it.  Little to no extra features.  The day with Soulja Boy was a waste of time for me and that young lady.  Soulja Boy reminds me of my youngest nephew, a big kid.
